There are 3 maim types of issues in Java:
1.Syntax( occur when java syntax is not followed, occur at compile time )To fix use your IDEs
2.Logical(occur when programs don't do things they supposed to do) to fix use Debugger
3.Exceptions(runtime) to fix read the error and take rhe help from the class exception is being thrown.



Exception Handling(finding and fixing runtime errors).
There are some keywords and blocks of code that we can use to avoid these exceptions.
There are some keywords and block of codes that we can use to avoid these exceptions.
try, catch, finally, throws, throw
